title: IFillPatternFeatureData.SkippedItemArray
description: Gets or sets the pattern instances to skip in this fill pattern feature.
returns: Array of pattern instances to skip (see Remarks )
remarks:
The array is linear and zero-based and contains the (row_id, column_id) of each pattern instance to skip.
For example,
[row_id_instance1, column_id_instance1, row_id_instance2, column_id_instance2, ...]
